steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit015" and Comment "Testing for checking empty and duplicate index"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit015" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol015" Type "integer" for Table name "jit015"
When I open add-index popup of table "jit015"
When I press Save button modal popup without wait
Then I should see inline error message of dropdown label Index column of Index number "1" has value "Column is required!!"
